'HATFUL OF RAIN' SOARS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was truly thrilled by the production of "A Hatful of Rain" at the Ensemble 
Theatre in Orange. 
</P>
<P>
 What a wonderful surprise to find that we have such a great little theater in 
this area and one that definitely should be better noticed by our 
theater-hungry public.The actor who played Johnny the eldest son (David 
Boreanaz) was so convincing that I totally forgot that we were only about 10 
people in the audience. This was truly a shame, since all the actors were 
wonderful in their delivery of this very physical play. 
</P>
