Mini-Revival will be held at 7 p.m. Wednesday, Thursday and Friday. The guest 
speaker will be the Rev. Nelson H. Smith of New Pilgrim Baptist Church in 
Birmingham, Ala. 4831 S. Gramercy Place, Los Angeles. (213) 296-5610. 
</P>
