Hill Harvester Church, a 10,000-member interracial congregation in Decatur, 
Ga., will speak at 7 p.m. Tuesday at Harvester Church of Temecula. His wife, 
Sandra Clements, who is a teacher and preacher, will also speak. The church, at 
Highway 79 and Anza Road, has its entry on Calle Arnaz. (909) 676-5684. 
