<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091794-0129 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 079987 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 17, 1994, Saturday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
