<P>
 The fourth anniversary of the Thomas F. Riley Terminal at John Wayne Airport 
will be marked with a public celebration from noon to 5 p.m. today. Among the 
highlights will be a fashion show of flight attendant uniforms dating from the 
1930s to the present. 
</P>
