<DATE>
<P>
September 17, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 10; Column 4; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
