<HEADLINE>
<P>
'STRANGE SNOW' MELTS STORM OF WAR INTO IMAGES OF LOVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By T.H. McCULLOH, SPECIAL TO THE TIMES 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
