</P>
<P>
 * "Strange Snow," Moulton Theatre, Laguna Playhouse, 606 Laguna Canyon Road, 
Laguna Beach. Tuesday through Friday, 8 p.m.; Saturday, 2 and 8 p.m.; Sunday, 2 
and 7 p.m. Ends Oct. 9. $13-$22. (714) 497-9244. Running time: 2 hours, 15 
minutes. Ron Campbell: Megs 
</P>
<P>
