<P>
BESCHEN ADVANCES AT LOWER TRENCHES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Defending champion Shane Beschen of San Clemente had the highest score Friday 
and received a 10 on one ride as he advanced in the main event of the Bud Surf 
Tour at Lower Trestles. 
</P>
