 Vice De La Pena of Laguna Niguel and Beschen's brother Gavin advanced along 
with Mike Parsons of San Clemente, Richie Collins of Newport Beach, Todd Miller 
of Costa Mesa and Jeff Deffenbaugh of Huntington Beach. 
</P>
