fumbled after catching a pass for a 14-yard gain. Moorpark took over with 1:03 
remaining at its 24. 
</P>
<P>
 Ocegueda rushed for 90 yards in 11 carries, including an eight-yard touchdown 
run. He also caught a 55-yard pass from James Cummings in the first half. 
</P>
<P>
 Cummings rushed for 92 yards in 12 carries, including a 52-yard dash in the 
second quarter. He also completed 12 of 19 passes for 131 yards and a 
touchdown. 
</P>
<P>
 Paul, Moorpark's junior quarterback, tied the score with a three-yard run on 
fourth and goal late in the third quarter. He finished with 66 yards in seven 
carries and completed eight of 12 passes for 125 yards with no interceptions. 
