<P>
 Century High quarterback Stanley Villanueva completed nine of 10 passes for 
184 yards and three touchdowns Friday night to pace the Centurions to a 33-7 
victory over John Glenn at La Mirada High. 
</P>
<P>
 The 5-10, 185-pound senior hit his first five passes before throwing an 
incompletion, but Century didn't miss much after that.The Centurions scored on 
their first two possessions of the game. 
</P>
