27-0 lead. 
</P>
<P>
 Glenn didn't get its first first down until the 6:05 mark of the second 
quarter. And the Eagles didn't complete their first pass until midway through 
the fourth quarter. 
</P>
<P>
 Rodriguez led Century in receiving with three catches for 62 yards and a 
touchdown. Jose Caravez finished with 47 yards in nine carries for the 
Centurions. RUSSELL BANKS 
