<BYLINE>
<P>
By MICHAEL LYNCH 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 El Modena running back Jason Said scored on a five-yard run late in the fourth 
quarter to give the Vanguards a 10-7 victory over Sunny Hills in a nonleague 
game Friday at Buena Park High School. 
</P>
<P>
 The crowd of 1,800 saw the lethargic Vanguard offense come to life in the 
second half and steal a victory from the Lancers. 
