<P>
DIGEST: FALL BASKETBALL REGISTRATION SET FOR TODAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The American Roundball Corporation is registering boys and girls in grades 3 
through 8 for fall basketball leagues from 10 to 11:30 a.m. today at North 
Hollywood High.  
</P>
<P>
 A second session of sign-ups is scheduled to take place the following Saturday 
at the same site. 
</P>
<P>
 Registration for boys and girls in grades 7 through 12 will take place the 
next two Sundays, Sept. 18 and 25, from 11 a.m. to 12:30 p.m. at North 
Hollywood High, and from 4 to 5:30 p.m. at Camarillo High. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: 818-995-3761. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 The Maccabiah basketball league will hold sign-ups on Sunday at Grant High at 
1 p.m.  
</P>
<P>
 There are divisions for boys and girls ages 8-13. Registration fee is $75. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: 818-783-5157. 
</P>
