 The Artists' defense was tested in the latter moments of the fourth quarter, 
when Hawley completed three passes of 25, 18 and 14 yards. With seconds ticking 
away, and no timeouts left, Hawley scrambled but was stopped at the Artists' 
four-yard line. An incomplete pass ended the threat. RICHARD MELKONIAN 
